{"tid":175440,"cid":25,"subCid":0,"title":"那些年，我係街遇過的主人們！","createTime":"2017-03-27T13:18:51.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-28T07:09:39.000Z","uid":29314,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"4a2b8dccb96e0069625ddb5884dda9f51aacab0a","tid":175440,"uid":29314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-27T13:18:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://holland.pk/0x1ize95\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2F0x1ize95&h=b419206f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n工廈一個雜貨貨倉養既小黑貓。<br />\n<br />\n成日係走廊鳩遊遊。<br />\n<br />\n有人行過就會喵喵叫。<br />\n<br />\n腳膠黎，你一停低就會勁磨你隻腳唔畀你走。"},{"pid":"46e2593ff68a9af1a7d477f7149dab4a6e5f90a7","tid":175440,"uid":29314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-27T13:22:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://holland.pk/efbgirwk\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fefbgirwk&h=5e36a51a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n住係公園入面既小黃貓。<br />\n<br />\n至鐘意tan係行人路晒太陽。<br />\n<br />\n野外求生能力好強。<br />\n<br />\n識捉麻雀黎食。"},{"pid":"0ffdc3f7bded2cb6d004409f7ab0334f45179bef","tid":175440,"uid":62822,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-27T13:22:58.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"ea9fb337433d3fc7e83bbee39a5fb0e48346b2f5","tid":175440,"uid":47819,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-27T13:23:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://holland.pk/efbgirwk\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fefbgirwk&h=5e36a51a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n住係公園入面既小黃貓。<br />\n<br />\n至鐘意tan係行人路晒太陽。<br />\n<br />\n野外求生能力好強。<br />\n<br />\n識捉麻雀黎食。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n食麻雀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"debd1ccdac71068bec1aa00c316df3be3e084a72","tid":175440,"uid":29314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-27T13:27:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://holland.pk/b0liy4ox\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fb0liy4ox&h=b2acdebb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n鄉郊地方既流浪貓一家。<br />\n<br />\n睇住佢由BB成長。<br />\n<br />\n一家都好瘦。雖然無人恰佢地，但勁怕人。<br />\n<br />\n擁有閃避流浪狗技能。<br />\n<br />\n最安全既地方就係鐵皮屋屋頂。多數係果度訓晏覺，同埋玩。"},{"pid":"83900ab339a8f0594194c5d18f71a6de32c94028","tid":175440,"uid":93091,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-27T13:29:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 無圖<br />\n係ssp見好多街貓，keep住收留左幾年，而家一屋七貓，仲多過人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fa25d565d5e4be863b06ceae4e7228d14550c3cb","tid":175440,"uid":20867,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-27T13:31:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/03/27/213111_697ed68e97a8e7cc82dd2646a8161259.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F03%2F27%2F213111_697ed68e97a8e7cc82dd2646a8161259.jpg&h=71e75d5e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"08401d1450eb628f9d6ab4ce87bb1fd151c43bfb","tid":175440,"uid":29314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-27T13:31:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://holland.pk/jldpxzke\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fjldpxzke&h=b7bd980a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n太子道西21X號一間花店地鋪養既貓。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n好肥美。<br />\n<br />\n外表文靜&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n直至你手多摸佢，佢會咬你！"},{"pid":"6926afd9b716698bebddc4724ec5f1769aaffd75","tid":175440,"uid":29314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-27T13:35:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://holland.pk/yf1udimx\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fyf1udimx&h=efa15c39&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n又一隻住係鄉郊地方既四腳踏雪。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n聰明，識得搵無人但有鐵絲網圍住既地方，<br />\n<br />\n完全無視網外既大狗，大覺訓！"},{"pid":"c52338bdd44bad939780d284e15e54b0eec3b73d","tid":175440,"uid":29314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-27T13:37:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>[]<a href=\"https://holland.pk/efbgirwk[/img]\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fefbgirwk%5B%2Fimg%5D&d=S%2FsiG%2FBE2bBILTWTz3VeJsVakpCEQgWe3bOYm8oES40%3D&h=2c9e84a2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://holland.pk/efbgirwk[/img]</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n住係公園入面既小黃貓。<br />\n<br />\n至鐘意tan係行人路晒太陽。<br />\n<br />\n野外求生能力好強。<br />\n<br />\n識捉麻雀黎食。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n食麻雀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/dcwo8rb3\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fdcwo8rb3&h=6f3870a9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n有圖為證！<br />\n<br />\n識得食，一定食新鮮麻雀！"},{"pid":"55f33dc02ce4b41649026453e066d278efe96eab","tid":175440,"uid":29314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-27T13:39:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://holland.pk/5b7pxryv\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2F5b7pxryv&h=bd324216&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n喵：「餵我啦！餵我啦！餵我啦！」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n係咪好想帶佢返屋企呢？"},{"pid":"818f4169fb96a96e991d09bdee1670f20afe72d9","tid":175440,"uid":29314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-27T13:42:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://holland.pk/s86coihd\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fs86coihd&h=a44ed48e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n$20/斤！   <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n唔通貓貓都濕熱？<br />\n<br />\n要訓係土伏苓隔離去濕？"},{"pid":"2d57b139c0206c8622078b59b8d7024450beed2c","tid":175440,"uid":68352,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-27T13:57:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://h